<!--
Problem Statement 5: Convert XML Data to HTML using XSLT with Computed Result and Filtering 
Develop an XSLT stylesheet to transform XML data into a well-formatted HTML page. 
Requirements: 
Create an XML file containing records of at least 4 students Each student record should include: 
•	Name 
•	Roll Number 
•	Marks / Percentage 
Do NOT store the “Result (Pass/Fail)” in XML. It must be calculated dynamically. 
XSLT Design: 
Design an XSLT file to: 
Extract student data from the XML file 




-->




<?xml version="1.0"?>

<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="student.xsl"?>

<students>

<student>
<name>Amit</name>
<roll>1</roll>
<marks>75</marks>
</student>

<student>
<name>Rahul</name>
<roll>2</roll>
<marks>35</marks>
</student>

<student>
<name>Neha</name>
<roll>3</roll>
<marks>80</marks>
</student>

<student>
<name>Pooja</name>
<roll>4</roll>
<marks>30</marks>
</student>

</students>